author: Kumalo M Khoisan
quote: "In the hush of the evening,"
subject: African Nature Poets (19th–Early 20th century)
permalink: /African Nature Poets (19th–Early 20th century)/Kumalo M Khoisan/Kumalo M Khoisan - Evenings Embrace
---

In the hush of the evening,
As shadows lengthen and grow,
The world wraps in a blanket,
Of whispers soft and low.

Each crag and crevice glistens,
With the dew of fading light,
And for a moment, we are one,
In the embrace of night.

- Kumalo M Khoisan
